sources.title: San Andreas Quake + San Andreas Mega Quake | 2 Full Action Disaster Movies | Double Feature
sources.description:
*San Andreas Quake* - When a discredited L.A. Seismologist warns of an impending 12.7 earthquake, no one takes her seriously. Now on her own, she races desperately to get her family to safety before the earthquake breaks Los Angeles apart from the mainland.
2015.  Stars: Jhey Castles, Jason Woods, Grace Van Dien

*San Andreas Mega Quake* - Scientists make a horrible discovery: The "Big One" is coming in two days, with it, California will sink to the ocean. Their only hope is to rupture a volcano that will displace the earthquake's energy and build a new crust on the surface. But as foreshocks turn California into chaos, it's a race against time the scientists might not win.
2019.  Stars: Joseph Michael Harris, Christie Nicholls, Liz Fenning
